<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><!-- end .ru-story -->
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Gilt Groupe Likely to Go Public This Year <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> Gilt Groupe, which has considered an initial public offering in the past, is expected to go public this year, likely in the third quarter, ReCode reports. Goldman Sachs will manage the offering.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//recode.net/2014/02/10/gilt-groupe-to-go-public-likely-in-third-quarter-ipo/"> RECODE </a></span></p>
</div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><!-- end .ru-story -->
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"> Chinese Pork Producer Enlists Banks for Help With I.P.O. <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> WH Group, the Chinese pork producer that acquired Smithfield Foods last year, has designated roles for 17 banks in its upcoming share sale, which aims to raise more than $6 billion, The Financial Times reports. The deal would be the biggest in Hong Kong since 2010.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/dfa5abce-9238-11e3-8018-00144feab7de.html#axzz2srjK5vXp"> FINANCIAL TIMES </a></span></p>
